Package: neuro2
Type: Package
Title: Neuropsychological Assessment Report Generator
Version: 0.1.8
Authors@R: person("Joey", "Trampush",
                  email = "joey.trampush@brainworkup.org",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0830-508X"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for generating neuropsychological
    assessment reports. Provides R6 classes for processing cognitive and
    behavioral test data, generating publication-quality tables and figures,
    and creating formatted reports using Quarto and Typst. Designed for
    pediatric and adult neuropsychological assessments.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/brainworkup/neuro2
